<H3> <TI>   Declaration Supported by Canadian Party </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Declaration Supported by Canadian Party </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK0306214094 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1506 GMT 3 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK0306214094 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, June 3 (KCNA) -- The National Committee 
of the Quebec Communist Party of Canada recently adopted a 
resolution supporting the Pyongyang declaration "Let us defend 
and advance the cause of socialism." 
  The resolution denounced the U.S. imperialists and the South 
Korean authorities' provocative acts of constantly threatening 
peace on the Korean peninsula. 
  Condemning the large-scale campaign against the DPRK over 
its 
"nuclear issue" as a move to destabilize the socialist Korea, 
the resolution expressed solidarity with the Korean people in 
their struggle for defence of socialism. 

</TEXT>

