<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-EAS-94-114 </AU>
Daily Report 
<DATE1>  11 Jun 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   `Immortal Feats' Performed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Immortal Feats' Performed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK1106110394 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1046 GMT 11 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1106110394 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["Great Feats of WPK in Achieving its Steel-like Unity and </F>
Cohesion" -- KCNA headline] 
  [Text] Pyongyang, June 11 (KCNA) -- The 30 years since the 
dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il assumed leadership over the 
party work is a brilliant history of an illustrious leader who 
has performed immortal feats in the efforts to increase the 
might of the singlehearted unity of the Workers' Party of Korea 
[WPK] in every way, says NODONG SINMUN in a signed article today 
on the lapse of 30 years since the dear leader began to lead the 
party. 
  It quotes the dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il as saying: 
  "Our party achieved solid unity and cohesion a long time 
ago. 
Not resting content with this, however, it has continued to work 
hard to strengthen the single-hearted unity of the whole party 
around the leader, so that it maintains unbreakable unity and 
cohesion, without any vacillation even in the present complex 
situation." 
  Referring to immortal feats performed by the dear leader in 
the struggle to strengthen the unity and cohesion of the WPK in 
every way, the article notes: 
  Of primary importance in his great leadership feats is that 
he has made it possible to firmly defend the tradition of the 
proud singlehearted unity and glorify it through generations. 
  From the first days of his leadership over the chuche cause 
of building the party he has subordinated all the party work and 
activities entirely to the work for firmly defending and 
exalting the tradition of singlehearted unity established by the 
great leader Comrade Kim Il-song when he started the Korean 
revolution. 
  Today when many parties of the world which had boasted of 
their long history have collapsed, not defending the tradition 
of unity, the WPK is firmly defending the tradition of 
singlehearted unity established in the initial period of the 
revolution. Herein lies the distinguished greatness and wise 
leadership of the dear leader. 
  What holds an important place in his great leadership feats 
is that he put forward the slogan of modelling the whole party 
on the chuche idea and has victoriously organized and led the 
struggle for its realisation, thus turning the WPK into an 
unbreakable integrated whole of one ideology and purpose. Thus, 
the organisational and ideological might of the WPK has 
increased immensely and a new change has taken place in the 
ideological and moral traits of the party members. 
  Today the entire party members think and act in accordance 
with the party's ideology and purpose at any time and in any 
place with the firm stand and view that they know nothing but 
the chuche idea, the revolutionary idea of the party. 
  What holds a brilliant place in his immortal leadership 
feats 
is also that he has made the whole party an entity of loyalty 
and filial piety, which is pervaded by unfailing loyalty to the 
party and the leader, with his great benevolent politics. 
  Regarding the idea of "believing in the people as in heaven" 
as his maxim from his early years, he always firmly believes in 
his revolutionary soldiers and people and spares nothing for 
them. 
  What holds a brilliant place also in his great leadership 
feats is that he has made sure that the work for strengthening 
the unity and cohesion of the party was conducted in close 
combination with the struggle to effect a great upswing in all 
domains of the revolution and construction and, thus, its 
indestructible vitality was demonstrated powerfully in practice. 
  In particular, the dear leader has seen to it that the whole 
party and the entire people vigorously conducted mass movements. 
This is a great contribution made by him to further 
strengthening the might of unity and cohesion of the party and 
effecting revolutionary changes in socialist construction. 
  The immortal feats of the dear leader who has exalted the 
might of singlehearted unity of the WPK on the highest level 
with his extraordinary intelligence, tested leadership and 
popular politics of warm love and trust in only 30 years which 
can be regarded a moment in the long history of the 
revolutionary movement, will shine forever with the victorious 
advance of the Korean-style socialism. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

