<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Soviet's Article Praises Kim Chong-il's Politics </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Soviet's Article Praises Kim Chong-il's Politics </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK1106153294 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1519 GMT 11 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1106153294 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, June 11 (KCNA) -- Former Soviet Army 
surgeon Mikhail Shulman recently published an article headlined 
"Benevolent Politics of Comrade Kim Chong-il Is Eternal 
Cornerstone of Unity and Victory". 
  In a lengthy article with subtitles "`We Serve the People 
Exclusively'" and "Even if the Earth Is Broken", the author says 
the dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il is confidently leading the 
whole party, all the people and the entire Army to the victory 
of socialism with his spirit of devoted service to the people, 
distinguished leadership ability and iron faith and will. 
  Shulman, far above 80, visited Korea several times from 
August 1945 when Korea was liberated from the colonial rule of 
Japanese imperialism. 
  He says: 
  What I cannot forget any moment among many unforgettable 
things in my life is the great personality and outstanding 
leadership ability of Comrade Kim Il-song and Comrade Kim 
Chong-il, the great leaders of the Korean people, and the 
brilliant looks of socialist Korea which is soaring imposingly 
above the clouds in the east. 
  Pointing to the superior health care system of Korea where 
doctors visit residents, before the patients come to them, 
everyone gets medical assistance without paying a penny, and is 
provided with all conditions for the promotion of health by the 
state, the author says: The noble human love, great human love 
of Comrade Kim Chong-il is, indeed, a panacea for the longevity 
of the people in good health. 
  He went on: 
  Korea which was a colonial agriculture country with backward 
economy for many years and, worse still, was reduced to ruins in 
a three-year war built solid foundations of an independent 
national economy diversely developed and equipped with modern 
technologies in a few years. This is a miracle and change which 
can be brought about only in Korea where everything serves the 
people and their strength is the driving force of social 
development. 
  The imperialists in the West are decrying the economy of 
Korea, alleging that it has gone bankrupt. But this is a 
sophism to mar the image of socialist Korea. 
  I fully grasped the greatness of the leader through the 
reality of Korea which is constantly developing politics, 
economy and culture with main emphasis on the ideological, 
material and cultural life of the people. 
  Comrade Kim Chong-il who is possessed of the quality, 
personality and ability to make everything serve the people, 
believing them as heaven, is, indeed, a man for the people, the 
greatest of the great. 
  There were in history great men who earned fame with wisdom, 
famous generals who earned fame with martial arts and 
politicians who won popular sentiments with benevolence. But 
none of these great men can be equal to the great personality of 
Comrade Kim Chong-il with literary and military accomplishments, 
loyalty and filial duty, iron will and grit. 
  Socialism collapsed in some countries at present. But Korea 
is firmly defending socialism and winning victory after victory, 
smashing the anti-socialist moves of the imperialists. 
  Now the people of many countries question what is the secret 
that Korea, not a big country, is fighting the United States 
singlehanded and overwhelming it thoroughly at a time when even 
influential politicians cringe if the U.S. shout at them. 
  I clearly saw the source of the strength of the Korean 
people 
while visiting Korea. 
  The singlehearted unity of the party and the popular masses 
united rock-firm around Comrade Kim Chong-il, supreme commander 
of the Korean People's Army, is the source of invincible might 
which can create something out of nothing and defeat any 
formidable enemy. 
  It is the distinguished merit of Comrade Kim Chong-il 
possessed of outstanding idea and theories and preeminent 
leadership ability that the singlehearted unity of Korea is so 
solid and virile as today. 
  The outstanding leadership of Comrade Kim Chong-il in 
strengthening the working-class party, the general staff of the 
revolution, enhancing the leadership role of the party in every 
way, effecting a fundamental turn in the building of the 
revolutionary Armed Forces and fully displaying the advantages 
of socialism in economy, culture and all other domains has 
instilled deep into the hearts of the entire people the firm 
faith and will that when they uphold his leadership, they can 
surely occupy any fortress in socialist construction, drive back 
the counterrevolutionary offensive of all the enemies and always 
win victory. The singlehearted unity of Korea is so powerful 
because the whole society is overflowing with this faith and 
will. 
  What I want to stress as regards the singlehearted unity of 
Korea is that it is a crystal of benevolent politics, politics 
of love and trust of dear Comrade Kim Chong-il. 
  The mighty unity of the entire people like the singlehearted 
unity of Korea can be achieved only by the strength of idea, the 
strength of politics and the strength of love of such 
illustrious leader as Comrade Kim Chong-il who enjoys undisputed 
trust of the people. 
  The Democratic People's Republic of Korea, a country guided 
by the illustrious leader, where the people is the master of the 
state and society and the singlehearted unity of the entire 
people has been achieved, will further prosper, displaying its 
might to the whole world as a fortress of socialism and a beacon 
of the hope of mankind. 

</TEXT>

