hesitation to the plaza of the national conference which will 
open a new chapter of national reconciliation and unity, 
irrespective of residence and job, if they to not want to fall a 
victim to big powers but really want the peace and peaceful 
reunification of the country, says NODONG SINMUN in a signed 
