at any cost and ignite a nuclear war against the North together 
with outside forces. This is an unpardonable criminal act which 
can be done only by such rare traitors and warmaniacs as the Kim 
Yong-sam group which takes no notice of the country and the 
nation, peace and peaceful reunification. 
  The Kim Yong-sam clique is trying to block the convocation 
of 
the national conference for national reconciliation and unity 
with sword-brandishing and war moves, but in vain. 
  Unshakable is the will of the 70 million fellow countrymen 
to 
convene the national conference and tide over the present 
difficulties and open the road of the country's peace and 
reunification. 

