<H3> <TI>   Soldiers Accelerate Construction of Expressway </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Soldiers Accelerate Construction of Expressway </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK1306082994 Pyongyang Korean Central Television Network in 
Korean 1100 GMT 11 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK1306082994 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang Korean Central Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Korean </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Upholding the party's intent to hasten the 
completion of the expressway between Pyongyang and Hyangsan, 
Korean People's Army soldiers of Comrade Choe Tong-suk's unit 
are vigorously accelerating the bridge construction assigned to 
them. 
  The unit soldiers, who have a firm faith to do everything 
the 
party decides, have completed placing some 40,000-cubic meters 
of gravel and building about 4,000-square meters of retaining 
walls and more than 10 structures by accelerating the 
construction with the revolutionary spirit of self-reliance and 
fortitude. They have also completed planting trees and grass. 
Being elated by the completion of these things, they are 
expediting the construction of the bridge and effect innovation 
every day. 
  In close cooperation with the working class at the No. 51 
construction office of the Hwanghae Steel Complex, they are now 
accelerating erecting (?pillars) and are scoring gains in this 
work by overcoming difficulties and obstacles with their own 
strength. 

</TEXT>

