be ranks of loyalty unfailingly faithful to the party and the 
leader, the speakers said it is one of big achievements in the 
efforts to model literature and art on the chuche idea. 
  Referring to the feats of the dear leader who established a 
regular system of guidance over the party life in the domain of 
literature and art, they stressed that it was a precious result 
of the new system's superiority and vitality that writers and 
artistes remain boundlessly loyal and devoted to the party and 
the leader. 

