<H3> <TI>   World Bank Grants Agriculture Loan </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    World Bank Grants Agriculture Loan </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK1406071294 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam in English 1000 GMT 13 
Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK1406071294 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi Voice of Vietnam </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Ten Vietnamese Southern peasant cities have received 
loans valued at $52 million from the World Bank to restore 
agriculture. The loans are aimed at restoring and developing 
agricultural services, giving financial credit to 50,000 farmer 
households, and restoring 150,000 hectares of rubber trees. 
They also help Vietnam provide trends and pioneer projects on 
the development of rural areas. 

</TEXT>

