<DOCNO> FBIS4-29005 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "dreas115_n_94018" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-EAS-94-115 </AU>
Daily Report 
<DATE1>  10 Jun 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> Vietnam </F>
<H3> <TI>   Party Members Expelled for Poor Conduct </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Party Members Expelled for Poor Conduct </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK1306082294 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network in Vietnamese 
1430 GMT 10 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK1306082294 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network </F>
<F P=105>  Vietnamese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] In implementing the party Central Committee's Third 
Plenum Resolution on renovating and revamping the party, party 
committee echelons in Ha Bac Province have satisfactorily 
screened party members to help them rectify shortcomings and 
mistakes. They also expelled from the party degenerated and 
deviant elements and those who violated discipline or acted at 
variance with party and state policies and lines. 
  So far, disciplinary measures have been taken against 6,000 
party members, including 2,200 who were expelled from the party 
for poor conduct. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

